thread.title: Christine Barnes
thread.title_full: Spa World Australia Pty Ltd reviewed by Christine Barnes

author: Christine Barnes
title: Christine Barnes
text: We are so pleased that Dot persisted with us at every show, until we purchased our new swim spa. We use it all the time. Our niece says it is great to ease pregnancy pains and she and her husband come over at least once a week. The whole family come over regularly and we're all enjoying the time together. Thank you for this wonderful addition to our home.
